{"lemma":"كَلْبَةُ","slug":"كَلْبَةُ","root":"ك.ل.ب","root_slug":"ك-ل-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ك-ل-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n37145","n37146"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%83%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"female equivalent of كَلْب (kalb): bitch (female dog)","tags":["feminine","form-of"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/kal.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n37145","headword_ar":"كَلْبَةٌ","root":"klb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thorny tree, destitute of branches:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) so called because it catches to [the garments of] those who pass by it, like a dog: (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a rugged tree, with branches standing out apart, and tough thorns."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small thorny plant, of the kind called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iros","text_ar":"شِرْس"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2627},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$kAEA","text_ar":"شكاعا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ukaAEaY","text_ar":"شُكَاعَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ukaAEap","text_ar":"شُكَاعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the description termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ukuwr","text_ar":"ذُكُور"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain thorny tree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the kind called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiDaAh","text_ar":"عِضَاه"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jrA'","text_ar":"جراء"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalibapN","text_ar":"كَلِبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalobatAani","text_ar":"كَلْبَتاَنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"implement with which the blacksmith takes hold of hot iron;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his forceps"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadiydapN *aAtu kalobatayoni","text_ar":"حَدِيدَةٌ ذَاتُ كَلْبَتَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An iron with two curved ends, forming a forceps"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. You also say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadiydataAni","text_ar":"حَدِيدَتَانِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*awaAtaA klbtyn","text_ar":"ذَوَاتَا كلبتين"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadaAy^idu *awaAtu klbtyn","text_ar":"حَدَايِدُ ذَوَاتُ كلبتين"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n37146","headword_ar":"كُلْبَةٌ","root":"klb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shop of a vintner."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, K.)       -A2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hairs that grow upon each side of the fore part of the nose and mouth"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a dog or cat: (Z, K:) wrongly explained as signifying the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nails"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a dog. (Z.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a strand"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAqap","text_ar":"طَاقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the fibres of the palm-tree"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liyf","text_ar":"لِيف"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which skins and the like are sewed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iqotafaA^a","text_ar":"اـِقْتَفَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or [so in the O and in the TA, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qfA^","text_ar":"قفا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but here, in the latter, instead of “ or, ” “ behind, ” which is evidently a mistake;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a strand"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAqap","text_ar":"طَاقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the fibres of the palm-tree, used in the same manner as the shoe-maker's awl that has, at its head, a perforation"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaqobN","text_ar":"ثَقْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so in the O, in the TA"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hjr","text_ar":"حجر"},{"kind":"text","text":"a strange mistranscription: what is meant is doubtless"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an eye,"},{"kind":"text","text":"like that of a needle, and it is by means of an implement with an eye at the end that the operation here described is commonly performed in the present day:] the thong, or the thread, or string, is inserted into the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"klbp","text_ar":"كلبة"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is doubled: thus it enters the place [or hole] of the sewing, and the sewer introduces his hand into the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idaAwap","text_ar":"اـِدَاوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q.v., i. e., the vessel upon which he is employed in working], and stretches the thong of leather, or the thread, or string, (O, L, TA,) in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"klbp","text_ar":"كلبة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L, TA.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalaba","text_ar":"كَلَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["Z","K","TA","O","L"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}